social_posts.post_text: This 2nd half of the year has been tough, and there are lots of things to fix that look like it'll carry over to Q1.  I gotta stay patient and not rush... and only look backward to make sure the same missed steps don't happen again.  Q1 and Q2 look very promising based on all the work and foundation thats been laid.  Everyone, send up some prayers for one another... for a happy holiday season, some joy, and fresh air! Hug your folks, make that a priority.  2023 on the way.
Let's End 2022 fresh and with a bang!

Greatful and Thankful.  I promise to enjoy every second good and bad. I just want to be able to say I enjoyed the ride... and my people all enjoyed me.  Hug and love ya ppl as much as possible.  We blessed. Capricorn 🐐

Happy Mother's Day.  Thankful for how I was raised and how my youngins being raised as well. Being a mother is probably one of the hardest things on earth, but it's handled with such grace!  Thankful for both of these beautiful women.

The district said they weren't sure little Devin could handle the gifted classes originally. Lmbo... we had to request a reassessment 2x. I always want my youth challenged. My youngin is exceptional, and I could tell off top. Welp, year one of those "accelerated classes" is done, and she did well.  A's in every subject for the entire year. #HonorRollStudent  Gone head, little DB! 😂 "Go have some fun and be creative today... let your imagination run wild." That's what I tell her every morning before she gets out of the car. 💯👑 #standupforyourkids
My 2. Them hugs have gotten me through some tough days!  Love you kiddo!
Thank you to anyone and everyone who's ever helped me or supported me in any way at any time.
